				{
					"value": "Regular Expression to match, (capture) and apply `scopeNames` to text  \n[VSCode TextMate](https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-textmate) uses the [Oniguruma](https://github.com/kkos/oniguruma/blob/v6.9.8/doc/RE) regex dialect  \n[TextMate 2.0](https://macromates.com/) uses the [Onigmo](https://github.com/textmate/Onigmo/blob/Onigmo-5.13.5/doc/RE) regex dialect  \n[Github-Linguist](https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist) uses the [PCRE](https://github.com/vmg/libpcre) regex dialect  \n[Shikijs](https://github.com/shikijs/shiki) uses the [JavaScript](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Regular_expressions) regex dialect  \n\n```json-textmate-regex\nExample: \\\\b(true|false)\\\\b\n```\n---\n[Translation](https://github.com/slevithan/oniguruma-to-es) from [Oniguruma](https://github.com/kkos/oniguruma/blob/master/doc/RE) to [JavaScript](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Regular_expressions): \n```javascript\n/\\\\[^\\n]/v\n```\n",
